The '''''Spacecaster''-class [[Shuttle/Legends|shuttle]]''' was a class of [[Starship/Legends|starship]] that was considered old and outdated by the standards of [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]]. Among its other components, these types of shuttles carried an [[Acceleration compensator/Legends|inertial compensator]], [[Ion engine/Legends|ion engines]], and a slow [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] unit. [[ExGal-4]]'s equipment included a Spacecaster; it was used by [[Danni Quee]] to repair an orbiting [[Telescope/Legends|telescope]]. The Spacecaster at the ExGal-4 facility was about 34 meters in length and about 30 meters in width.

